headline: Trane Technologies to Present at the Oppenheimer Industrial Growth Conference
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, April 29, 2025--Trane Technologies plc (NYSE: TT) a global climate innovator, today announced that company leadership will participate in a virtual fireside chat at the Oppenheimer Industrial Growth Conference. They will speak at 11:15 a.m. ET on Monday, May 5, 2025.
